title: Bid on the first Botto, up to 120 E
body:
I'm thinking we should bid on the first Botto, though the first one will prob go for several 100E - https://superrare.com/artwork-v2/asymmetrical-liberation-29715

It's been discussed on here before - the art is AI-generated and community curated. The mechanism is similar to Nouns but they mint & auction only once a week so prices might go even higher. With the airdrop they did, I think lot of whales will be bidding. 

I think it's v unikely we'll get it but I'd bid up to 120E? Would be like owning the first noun. Wdyt? At least we'd get the jenny name out there on the bid list.
author: 0x818cF89054B3A5E03D4677b52982E8319D009194
